{"tid":965161,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【恐怖國度】英女遊客五星級酒店按摩 疑遭按摩師性侵","createTime":"2019-01-01T22:24:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-02T01:36:00.000Z","uid":54337,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"2021ab59776d09b803f29b71c4eaab81384e0483","tid":965161,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T22:24:32.000Z","msg":"【恐怖國度】英女遊客五星級酒店按摩 疑遭按摩師性侵<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190101/59092831\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190101%2F59092831&d=4nIA3IbJeVg%2FUN0DUWkZ0L%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=a4255edd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190101%2F59092831&h=932c5cdd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190101/59092831</a>"},{"pid":"61e5178d20c547d09f3afe0c62db4b30aa5ffd7a","tid":965161,"uid":54337,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T22:25:03.000Z","msg":"印度再次爆出涉及外國遊客的性侵案，一名英國女遊客日前在當地的5星級酒店接受按摩服務後，聲稱被按摩師性侵，目前疑犯正被通緝。<br />\n<br />\n一名54歲英籍女遊客報稱上月20日在昌迪加爾（Chandigarh）一間5星級酒店接受按摩服務時，遭年約20多歲的男按摩師非禮及性侵，包括用手指插入其下體。<br />\n<br />\n警方將案件列作強姦案處理，指疑犯現已逃離昌迪加爾，正被通緝。該名女遊客在事發當天已向酒店投訴，但她在完成西姆拉（Shimla）之旅後，才於12月27日正式報警。其後她接受醫療檢查及在裁判官見證下錄口供。警方指已翻查閉路電視及電話紀錄，追緝疑犯的下落。"},{"pid":"eb0984b07eacdd5cb0f182bcf5237c82cadb5502","tid":965161,"uid":55913,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T00:21:32.000Z","msg":"54歲鬼婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d10807b490156b680194830ac5ee8e4b6b3f84f6","tid":965161,"uid":54337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T00:22:47.000Z","msg":"咖哩 = 強姦大國"},{"pid":"0e2e1744d53395d17595b909cbd66e1ac1d7f97e","tid":965161,"uid":30788,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T